metadata.name: Nils Frahm
metadata.description:
Nils Frahm live at the Barbican, London

Shot on Kodak Tri-X 400 35mm film  

Leica M6 camera with the lovely creamy 35 mm Summilux lens that was made in the 1960's in Canada.
